{"tid":2008291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(投訴師入) 清算註冊社工 郭偉强","createTime":"2020-05-09T02:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T11:22:01.000Z","uid":111929,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"763a325d2fc2e73670beb70ce1b22670dfd67d15","tid":2008291,"uid":111929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好意思 係社畜先啱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港社會工作者總工會 (HKSWGU)<br />\n16 小時前<br />\n<br />\n本會收到多位同工及巿民表示於今午的立法會直播片段內，目擊註冊社工 #郭偉强 涉嫌從後強拉陳志全的衣領至倒地，並拖行逾十米，向本會查詢投訴社工的途徑。社總現提供有關之直播片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/3190411130989821/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F3190411130989821%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=2b5b9b9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/3190411130989821/</a><br />\n如認為註冊社工郭偉强違反社工守則，可到此參閱投訴程序及下載投訴表格：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swrb.org.hk/tc/Content.asp?Uid=75\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swrb.org.hk%2Ftc%2FContent.asp%3FUid%3D75&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=995ebe51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swrb.org.hk/tc/Content.asp?Uid=75</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcNBZD1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxcNBZD1.jpg&h=0ce87c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kt1ZXqG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKt1ZXqG.png&h=273143dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1mOQLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1mOQLH.jpg&h=86d819a8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖片來源：100毛、香港電台、社工註冊局、立法會<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 留意唔係郭偉強，係郭偉强👈🏻簡體字。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKSocialWorkersGeneralUnion/posts/2884268658295534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKSocialWorkersGeneralUnion%2Fposts%2F2884268658295534&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=46513b4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKSocialWorkersGeneralUnion/posts/2884268658295534</a>"},{"pid":"2f0517700f22c31f7f31b09ff6d4d793eeb4e91c","tid":2008291,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:50:58.000Z","msg":"社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402b141541206a4f5babf7383bac60130a685e38","tid":2008291,"uid":111929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾影衰哂社福界 咁撚樣都做到實工 出實習讀咁多書讀屎片DLLM"},{"pid":"f76cdc25a6ef459397533c93468edb5d12bc7420","tid":2008291,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:52:32.000Z","msg":"【高手過招】政治專家教你打贏輿論戰 同藍絲鬧交成日鬧輸嘅你一定要睇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2005539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2005539</a><br />\n<br />\n35+爭取嚟做咩？35+就係攞嚟<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>罷免港共政府</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n「如果美國要求中國就中共病毒賠償，中國一定會攞各位香港人血汗錢嚟找數」</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「如果啲一帶一路投資失敗啲非洲國家要賠償，中國一定都會攞各位香港人血汗錢嚟找數」<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">GET MY MONEY BACK<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要攞返我啲錢<br />\n香港人啲錢唔係比港共亂咁洗</span></span><br />\n香港納稅人財政儲備 不是中共提款機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要攞返我啲錢</span></strong></span>」就係我哋對攬炒嘅論述<br />\n「<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>如果這是攬炒，我們不怕承認</strong></span></span>」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港財政儲備絕對唔可以比中共當係提款機嚟用<br />\n唔可以攞嚟起啲濕鳩明日大嶼<br />\n唔可以攞嚟找一帶一路啲數 債務<br />\n更加唔可以攞香港啲錢嚟賠償中共病毒索償費用</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n高鐵已經有版我哋睇<br />\n高鐵造價853億沒有帶來經濟效益 卻只有贈送中共病毒（武漢肺炎）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-10_NQdC3_1200x0.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n攬抄 就是從港共手中搶返屬於我哋嘅血汗錢<br />\n<br />\n立法會35+之後就係要否決預算案<br />\n推冧港共之後再建立一個<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>民主主權國家<br />\n35+就是「罷免港共行動」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n中國係中共病毒疫情之後將會比全球杯葛<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聰明嘅香港人要及時止蝕同中國割席<br />\n因為一個民主主權國家<br />\n係國際舞台先會有競爭力<br />\n先至可以同鄰近嘅星加坡，台灣一較高下</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港只要唔係民主主權國家，人哋係唔撚會show你，亦都唔會有信心返嚟香港投資</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n攬炒就是<br />\n「從港共手中搶回屬於香港人金庫」<br />\n「建立民主主權國家  才是爭取國際競爭力的致勝之道」"},{"pid":"7bead08c22de9d2c549d22d1dc6f850bd92dbfdb","tid":2008291,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:52:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b644bf5a26e9f8493c9c188c976ca7edfa059d3","tid":2008291,"uid":111929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"5c85349e20df807ce1b9c79fc2e65acb2685df12","tid":2008291,"uid":111929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"ab705213b6a6244e3aee05fb74def3863129bd13","tid":2008291,"uid":111929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"