,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb9b3bd70ae479228c25b385037293df3c9aa387","tid":2008291,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c039f87cf6aae7ad2d6ffff3db269e4bbc66c1af","tid":2008291,"uid":111929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acddfd903c35d3a8345551f0feec600b273c4ea2","tid":2008291,"uid":80496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"街頭抗爭呢個階段其實已經冇乜用，搞革命應該搞東印度公司，海外建軍。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2007554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2007554</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人對武力有點誤解 其實譬如阿富汗 美軍是支援出來的<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1962461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1962461</a><br />\n<br />\n721啟發：我地必須要有獨立武裝單位懲治黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pgjxGcX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pgjxGcX</a><br />\n<br />\n發展海外武裝組織<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2007770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2007770</a>"},{"pid":"17965f4b4f51ca34ff64156fd33e5991c542f437","tid":2008291,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e1e7a2362098c97b51ba080dece5be8bd64e3d9","tid":2008291,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9800e1272720861331290105d9d6d1a20ec72f31","tid":2008291,"uid":111929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4114c1cd15c3633e3a8a787a8473e740a1df4586","tid":2008291,"uid":288093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T10:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vkoNph2.jpg\" data-thu